What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I would recommend it, because if you want to learn Chinese this is the way to go. I'd describe it as high intensity, high reward kind of class. Lots of memorization. And I'd only recommend it to people that would consider learning Chinese in the long haul because otherwise it's just too much committed time.
